1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science reveals secrets about blocked practice limits that social media gets wrong.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,400
Blocked practice means repeating the same skill without variation.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:11,600
But, is that the best way to learn?

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:18,000
Studies show that while blocked practice can build confidence, it doesn’t prepare you for real challenges.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,400
In contrast, varied practice—mixing skills—enhances retention and adaptability in real scenarios.

6
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:27,200
So, while social media glorifies repetition, true mastery lies in embracing variety.

7
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,200
Want to master your skills?

8
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:30,800
Start mixing it up!

9
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:33,200
Like and follow for more insights.
